{"tid":2078281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國有地方政府允許有色人種豁免強制口罩令","createTime":"2020-06-25T02:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T03:52:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e227261ad299a07d3c43dfb36ee46c4ee2362b30","tid":2078281,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"2020-06-25 09:47:44<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕佛洛伊德之死在全美爆發大規模平權示威潮，引起廣泛迴響，然而，美國奧勒岡州林肯郡頒布的一項規定卻引發爭議<br />\n<br />\n.........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，美國各州陸續重啟商業、社交活動，為防止疫情再次爆發，林肯郡強制要求民眾在公共場所，無論室內室外都須戴上口罩，但為了避免種族歸納（racial profiling）疑慮，有色人種可不必遵守口罩強制令。<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，林肯郡約有5萬居民，其中9成是白人，黑人僅佔不到1成，但郡內有一個印地安人保留區，拉丁裔居民也逐漸增加。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3208561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3208561&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=1a97fa2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3208561&h=93773b25\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3208561</a>"},{"pid":"db219c6b7274caf92070ffbb9b96a18b59345a2d","tid":2078281,"uid":81273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:40:45.000Z","msg":"黃人贏返次 痴金慷"},{"pid":"add9ecdc74aaff59e6e2956d0039f0dcc3ede61c","tid":2078281,"uid":231886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:42:45.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f529de0a8b882fd4f4342c0b782f91ba6b738b","tid":2078281,"uid":273991,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"唔通有色人種唔會中肺炎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99795aa7f974767b7d